{"tid":1988963,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"sigma點睇全亞洲最大型的綜合電競館？","createTime":"2020-04-25T14:33:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T14:33:28.000Z","uid":321610,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ccb8dc29f6baed482bf02a2673437215de49f457","tid":1988963,"uid":321610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T14:33:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tN2Vg2f9zvw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtN2Vg2f9zvw&d=5PHCsmqc8bXRSfVPwy6hKuQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=a5c5d229\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tN2Vg2f9zvw</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200424/2UNZSNBI6BKUUYGISAH4PLUE7E/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_appledailyatm&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200424%2F2UNZSNBI6BKUUYGISAH4PLUE7E%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_appledailyatm%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=5PHCsmqc8bXRSfVPwy6hKuQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=dbc55171\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200424%2F2UNZSNBI6BKUUYGISAH4PLUE7E%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_appledailyatm%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=cdc776b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200424/2UNZSNBI6BKUUYGISAH4PLUE7E/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_appledailyatm&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n「其員工早前在YouTube揭露現時的經營情況，夾公仔已成主要收入來源」<br />\n<br />\n當當一間亞洲最大型的綜合電競館，仲要係香港首間達到GeForce 3星認證的電競館。今日竟然要靠夾公仔機維生？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nProfessor Sigma 多年醉心香港以及世界嘅電競業發展，對電競產業鏈有獨到見解，洞悉市場人士嘅枱底操作。<br />\n<br />\n雖然最近將焦點投放係本土文化同社會風氣。想透過教育廣大網民正確使用互聯網嘅方法，重塑一個更潔淨更有內涵嘅香港。<br />\n<br />\n不過相信重返電競老本行難唔到professor sigma嘅。小弟等緊professor sigma拍片指點香港電競館江山，撥正電競產業鏈發展！唔可以俾慕容公子依d花生之輩、奶頭娛樂之徒扭曲電競界嘅風氣，借電競之名招搖撞騙！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}